'''希臘陸龜'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Testudo graeca''）是[[陸龜屬|陸龜屬]]下的一種[[龜|龜]]，分佈於南歐、北非和西南亞。現已確認其至少有20個[[亞種|亞種]]。摩洛哥和西班牙等国禁止交易希腊陆龟，但当地种群仍因非法宠物贸易而受到威胁。<ref>{{Cite journal |author=Pérez, I. |author2=Tenza, A. |author3=Anadón, J.D. |author4=Martínez-Fernández, J. |author5=Pedreño, A. |author6=Giménez, A|date=2012|title=Exurban sprawl increases the extinction probability of a threatened tortoise due to pet collections|journal=Ecological Modelling|volume=245|pages=19–30|doi=10.1016/j.ecolmodel.2012.03.016|hdl=10261/67281}}</ref><ref name="Bergin">{{cite web|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/267748463|title=Open, Unregulated Trade in Wildlife in Morocco's Markets, TRAFFIC Bulletin|author=Bergin|author2=Nijman|date=2014|accessdate=23 March 2015|archive-date=2018-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031133219/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/267748463|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author=Nijman, V|author2=Bergin, D|date=2017|title=Trade in spur-Thighed tortoises Testudo graeca in Morocco: Volumes, value and variation between markets|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/318456632|journal=Amphibia-Reptilia|access-date=2020-11-29|archive-date=2021-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107093404/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/318456632_Trade_in_spur-Thighed_tortoises_Testudo_graeca_in_Morocco_Volumes_value_and_variation_between_markets}}</ref>

